Phylosophy:
    1. Changes should be atomic. Check all things before changing anything.




tman structure
    tman         - main module. Handle user commands and options
    env          - display and manipulate environments

core:
    git          - manipulate task repos
    struct       - manipulate task structure
    taskid       - display and manipulate task IDs
    config       - display and manipulate system and user configs
    taskunit     - display and manipulate task units


